1993;;House of Cards;;American;;Michael Lessac;;Kathleen Turner, Tommy Lee Jones;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/House_of_Cards_(1993_film);;Following the death of her husband, Ruth Matthews moved her family to a quiet suburb, hoping to put the past behind them. While her son Michael is able to adapt, her daughter, Sally, is apparently traumatized by the experience and starts displaying unusual behavior. Ruth is later court mandated to see Jake Beerlander, an expert in child autism, to help Sally.